      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle remains in a showroom-state, exhibiting no discernible wear and maintaining its original factory luster. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been fastidiously maintained to ensure an experience identical to its initial delivery. For the discerning buyer who accepts only the absolute finest, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
