    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine, delivering 333 hp with a 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis is exceptional; the rear subframe has been professionally inspected and reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping and bushing elasticity, providing the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation and an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation. Mechanically synchronized and cosmetically flawless, this E46 represents the zenith of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
